            "title": "Google發布AI代理工具 強攻企業市場迎戰OpenAI",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Cw6AYRWaCvZNG7g9DSZc7A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/no/cnyes_hk_559/d4d59484fb843d974b6e63fc5389719b\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
