        {
            "title": "危機加深之時 Blue Owl嘗試了一場高風險突圍",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"摄影：迈克尔·纳格尔/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/KHaruyowjLUPiPQYYFi2JA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/7f7fe9a61cff3e9fc4cf8d05ca094831\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">摄影：迈克尔·纳格尔/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 在華爾街，幾乎沒有哪家公司比<span>Blue Owl</span> Capital更需要一場勝利。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">短短幾周內，隨著私募信貸市場壓力加大，這家公司迅速成為投資者審視的焦點。其股價已暴跌近50%；客戶正試圖從其基金中贖回前所未有的大額資金；激進投資者和做空機構也開始紛紛出手。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">就在這時，摩根士丹利提出了一項建議。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Blue Owl攝影：邁克爾·納格爾/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8o632.XOkExjFTyY8g4Msw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/72a565fe18d2f2c3a32107f1609a14df\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Blue Owl攝影：邁克爾·納格爾/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據知情人士透露，其投銀團隊已向多家資金管理機構摸底，評估潛在債券發行的需求，並認為有空間完成這筆交易。這不僅是籌資手段，更能向市場證明Blue Owl仍具備進入資本市場的能力，鞏固其投資級地位，並將其與一些最受尊敬的機構投資者聯繫在一起。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-baa5d046-db42-3061-b358-2212d2b56fac-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但代價是：公司必須提供更高的殖利率溢價才能促成交易。最終，高管層認為，為重建投資者信心，這點代價是值得的。而目前來看，這筆交易確實起到了效果。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自上周完成發債以來，Blue Owl股價已上漲17%；其上市的業務發展公司Blue Owl Capital Corp.（代碼OBDC）是本次債務發行主體，其股價上漲5.3%。根據彭博定價顯示，2028年到期債券的利差已收窄約25個基點。當品浩(Pimco)全數買下這筆4億美元債券時，動能進一步得到強化。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">SanJac Alpha首席投資官Andrew Wells稱，這是一筆「相當紮實的交易」，尤其是在當前私募信貸領域對放貸標準以及對易受人工智能衝擊的軟件公司敞口存在廣泛擔憂的背景下。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他說，「當像Pimco這樣的機構來接盤這類交易時，我認為這是一個很大的利好。他們很專業，懂得如何給市場定價，而這筆交易能夠完成，本身就是一個積極信號。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Blue Owl、摩根士丹利和Pimco的代表均拒絕對此發表評論。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題As Blue Owl’s Strains Worsened, Its Bankers Pitched a Long Shot</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Caleb Mutua.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8D%B1%E6%A9%9F%E5%8A%A0%E6%B7%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%99%82-blue-owl%E5%98%97%E8%A9%A6%E4%BA%86-%E5%A0%B4%E9%AB%98%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E7%AA%81%E5%9C%8D-135403137.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-22 22:35:11",
